title: Hawkwind - BBC4 documentary 'Do not Panic' (2007)
description:
This is an alternative torrent to the one uploaded by someone in 2007, to enable people that missed out to start a fresh grab.

I know that&#039;s a bit tedious, but at least I can seed the thing pretty much 24/7, and now I&#039;ve created a torrent file, I&#039;ll be able to re-seed in the future.

There&#039;s contributions from loads of ex-Hawks so well worth watching. House, Turner, Lemmy and Moorcock are the main ones that spring to mind. Also Doug Smith.

Anyone hoping to hear/see Dave Brock&#039;s input, forget it, as he didn&#039;t take part in the making of this documentary. But it covers their history pretty well ... or as well as you CAN cover 38 years in 50 minutes!!

NOTE: the VIDEO_TS folder plays fine on a computer but I haven&#039;t tried burning it off to DVD.
